            <p>If you want to share macros with other members of your team, you can send them the Macros file (in the Macros folder). If you have also added shortcuts that you want to share, you can send the Commands_3.mccmds file (in the AppData\Roaming\MadCap Software\<MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> folder). They can add these files to their AppData folder to use your macros or shortcuts.</p>
